high_descs: Turn around and walk to the dresser.
Pick up the blue phone from the front of the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Place the phone on the bed in front of the pillow.
Turn around and walk to the grey chair to the right of the dresser.
Pick up the phone from the chair.
Turn around and walk back to the bed.
Place the phone to the right of the other phone on the bed.
anns.task_desc: Place two phones on a bed.

high_descs: move forward a two feet and turn to the right and move to face the right side of the dresser
pick up the cell phone from the right corner of the dresser
turn around and move toward the bed
put the cell phone on to the bed in front of the green cushion
turn around and move to the gray chair that is to the right of the dresser
pick up the cell phone from the seat of the chair
turn around and move toward the bed
put the cell phone on to the bed to the right of the cell phone that is in front of the green cushion
anns.task_desc: put two cell phones on to the bed

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the right side of the dresser.
Pick up the cell phone.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Place the cell phone on the bed in front of the closest pillow.
Turn around and walk to the chair ahead and slightly to the right.
Pick up the cell phone on the chair.
Turn around and walk back to the bed.
Place the cell phone on the bed to the right of the first cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones on a bed.

high_descs: Turn to your left, then walk to the dresser on your right.
Pick up the cell phone on the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Put the cell phone on the bed next to the pillow.
Turn around and walk to the chair.
Pick up the cell phone on the chair.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Put the cell phone on the bed to the right of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones on the bed.

high_descs: Walk to the black drawers on your right.
Grab the blue smart phone on top of the black drawers.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Place the blue smart phone on the bed.
Turn around and walk to the gray lounge chair.
Grab the blue smart phone on the gray lounge chair.
Turn around and walk to the bed.
Place the blue smart phone to the right of the previous blue smart phone.
anns.task_desc: Place both of the blue smartphones on the bed.

high_descs: Turn right and walk until you are looking at the dresser across from the bed and face the right hand side of the dresser.
Pick up the blue smart phone on top of the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the bed and face the left side of the foot of the bed.
Place the phone on the bed spread under the pillow near the foot.
Turn around and walk to the chair so you are facing it.
Pick up the blue smartphone on the chair cushion.
Walk back to the foot of the bed where you were before.
Place the blue smartphone to the right of the other blue smartphone.
anns.task_desc: Place two smartphone on the foot of the bed.
